          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Planning that feels personal, polished, and grounded",
            "size": "4xl"
          }
        },
        "about-text-01": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Everafter was built for couples who want thoughtful guidance, a strong design point of view, and a planning experience that never feels louder than the celebration itself.</p>",
            "size": "lg"
          }
        },
        "about-text-02": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We believe the most memorable weekends feel effortless to the people attending them. That ease is never accidental. It comes from careful structure, clear communication, and design choices that belong to the couple rather than the planner.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "muted": true
          }
        }
      },
